---
title: Parmesan Pan-Fried Gnocchi with Spinach and Peas
description: Golden pan-fried gnocchi add a delicious twist to a classic Alfredo! Rich cream, cream cheese and savoury Parmesan make a luscious sauce for this vegetarian supper.
